<p><a name="Correspondence_with_dominical_letter" id="Correspondence_with_dominical_letter"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Doomsday_rule&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9" title="Edit section: Correspondence with dominical letter">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Correspondence with dominical letter</span></h2>
<p>Doomsday is related to the <a href="/wiki/Dominical_letter" title="Dominical letter">dominical letter</a> of the year as follows.</p>
<table class="wikitable" style="margin: 1em auto 1em auto">
